    #support-us.page(data-nosnippet)
        h1 Support Us
        p.title.is-size-3 Your donations help!
        p Vocabustudy is a free website, but donations do serve a purpose. #[span(style="font-weight: 600") Your ability to donate won't affect how you are treated on the site.]
        p Donating helps us with paying the $12 domain and working towards improving infrastructure.
        p.subtitle.is-size-5 How can you help out?
        .tabs-wrapper
            .tabs.is-large.is-toggle.is-primary
                ul
                    li.is-active
                        a Support us for free!
                    li
                        a Electronic Donation
                    li
                        a Physical Donation
            .tabs-content
                ul
                    li.is-active
                        p.title.is-size-3 Support us #[span(style="font-weight: 600") for free!]
                        p Can't donate? No problem! You can help us just as much by doing the following:
                        br
                        ul
                            p.li-tab #[strong Share Vocabustudy with your friends] and family. The more people who use Vocabustudy, the more we can improve it.
                            p.li-tab #[strong Report bugs] and #[strong request features] on #[a(href="https://github.com/For-0/vocabustudy") Vocabustudy's GitHub page]. The more bugs we find, the more stable the site will be.
                            p.li-tab #[strong Follow us!] Create a GitHub account and consider clicking the star button on #[a(href="https://github.com/For-0/vocabustudy") Vocabustudy's GitHub page]. This helps us get more attention to the project.
                            p.li-tab #[strong Use Vocabustudy] and be sure to comment and like sets. Your comments and likes motivate creators to make more sets.
                            p.li-tab #[strong Make sets!] Making sets will help other people learn. The more sets we have, the more useful Vocabustudy will be.
                    li
